Package: remote-sudo-touch
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Paul Kelaita
Depends: bash, python3
Recommends: openssh-client
Description: RemoteSudoTouch PAM helper for approving sudo via a Mac Touch ID bridge
 Installs the Ubuntu-side PAM helper that connects to localhost:9876,
 where a reverse SSH tunnel forwards requests to the macOS RemoteSudoTouch
 agent running behind Touch ID.
